import React from 'react'
import Home from './components/Home'
import "slick-carousel/slick/slick.css";
import "slick-carousel/slick/slick-theme.css";

import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch } from 'react-router-dom'


const App = () => {
    return ( <
        div >
        <
        Router >
        <
        Switch >
        <
        Home path = "/"
        exact / >
        <
        /Switch> <
        /Router> <
        /div>
    )
}

export default App
